ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO (1) the Hon. PETER D. LAUWERS from November 21 to 25, 2016, inclusive; (2) the Hon. HEATHER SMITH on November 30, 2016, and from December 2 to 4, 2016, inclusive; and (3) the Hon. MICHAEL H. TULLOCH on December 1, 2016.
